{"tid":1536691,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖aa制一問","createTime":"2019-09-03T16:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T03:39:34.000Z","uid":158949,"like":5,"dislike":65,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"78624f504f9f59065dbe0695d1bdb4bf5dc5cdd2","tid":1536691,"uid":158949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"拍左1年拖，現在收入都ok, 30k左右。女朋友同我同年，17k度。佢屋企條件差啲，我同佢比家用都一樣，係5k度。<br />\n<br />\n問題就嚟啦，由拍拖開始到現在，好多時出街都係我比錢，間唔中先象徵式咁收返佢少少。有時佢要買啲野，我幫佢比著先，問佢攞返錢，又要提佢先比。不過佢唔會要求去啲貴地方，去旅行都會share返，我6佢4咁。<br />\n<br />\n但係心理好似唔係好平衡，因為我有草錢的，草差不多半份糧，而佢係無草錢嘅。<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打覺得係咪應該同佢講要aa返？唔知會唔會令佢覺得我好小家。。。但係拍拖aa唔係正常ga 咩。。？"},{"pid":"dc1cbe27a4f4d60c8fca225d3bab726fb3847ee0","tid":1536691,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T16:56:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</stro